<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= seo ? seo.title : 'Agrim Classes' %></title>
<meta name="description" content="<%= seo ? seo.desc : 'Best Coaching Institute in Deoli' %>">
<meta name="keywords" content="<%= seo ? seo.keywords : 'education, coaching' %>">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css?v=1.1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>

    <script src="header.js"></script>
    <my-header></my-header>

 <section class="breadcrumb-area">

        <div class="shape-globe">
            <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFA500" stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                <path d="M2 12h20"></path>
                <path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z">
                </path>
            </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="shape-loop">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" stroke="#C4C6E5" stroke-width="12"
                stroke-linecap="round">
                <path d="M30,20 Q60,5 80,40 T50,90 T20,60" />
            </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="shape-scribbles">
            <svg width="80" height="100" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" stroke="#FFC07F" stroke-width="3">
                <path d="M80,10 Q90,20 85,30 T90,50" />
                <path d="M60,15 Q70,5 75,25 T80,40" />
                <path d="M90,5 Q100,15 95,25 T100,45" />
            </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="container">
            <div class="banner-content align-left">
                <span class="sub-heading">Agrim Classes</span>
                <h1 class="page-title">NTSE (National Talent Search Exam)</h1>
                <ul class="breadcrumb-list">
                    <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                    <li class="separator"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></li>
                    <li>Courses</li>
                    <li class="separator"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></li>
                    <li class="active">NTSE</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

<section class="course-intro-creative">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="intro-grid">
            <div class="intro-main">
                <span class="section-tag">Unlock Your Potential</span>
                <h2 class="creative-heading">Nurturing India's Future <span class="highlight">Talent</span></h2>
                <p class="creative-desc">
                    The National Talent Search Examination (NTSE) is a prestigious scholarship exam conducted by NCERT to identify and nurture talented students. Agrim Classes provides specialized coaching designed to help Class 10 students excel in both Stage I (State Level) and Stage II (National Level) of this highly competitive examination.
                </p>
                
                <div class="highlight-box">
                    <h4><i class="fas fa-award"></i> Scholarship & Recognition</h4>
                    <p>
                        Clearing NTSE not only provides financial scholarship up to Ph.D. level but also gives immense recognition. It builds a strong foundation for future competitive exams like JEE and NEET by developing strong analytical skills early on.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="intro-features">
                <div class="feature-card-small">
                    <div class="icon-circle"><i class="fas fa-brain"></i></div>
                    <h5>MAT & SAT Mastery</h5>
                    <p>Comprehensive coverage of both Mental Ability Test (MAT) and Scholastic Aptitude Test (SAT) with expert faculty guidance.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card-small">
                    <div class="icon-circle"><i class="fas fa-layer-group"></i></div>
                    <h5>Stage-Specific Focus</h5>
                    <p>Tailored strategies for state-level nuances in Stage I and national-level depth concepts in Stage II.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="boosters-section">
    <div class="" style="margin-left: 70px; margin-right: 70px; padding-top: 60px;">
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <h2 class="main-heading">Exam Preparation Boosters</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="boosters-grid">
            <div class="booster-card card-red">
                <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fas fa-user-friends"></i></div>
                <h4>India's Best<br>Ever Team</h4>
            </div>

            <div class="booster-card card-green">
                <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fas fa-database"></i></div>
                <h4>Small Batch Size<br>(Special 20)</h4>
            </div>

            <div class="booster-card card-dark-blue">
                <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fas fa-book-open"></i></div>
                <h4>Doubt Clearing<br>Session</h4>
            </div>

            <div class="booster-card card-light-blue">
                <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="far fa-building"></i></div>
                <h4>Complete Study Package<br>(Online | Offline)</h4>
            </div>

            <div class="booster-card card-grey">
                <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fas fa-download"></i></div>
                <h4>Fortnight<br>Test</h4>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="eligibility-section">
    <div class="" style="margin-left: 70px; margin-right: 70px;">
        <h3 class="table-title">NTSE Exam Overview</h3>
        
        <div class="table-wrapper">
            <table class="eligibility-table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th class="th-criteria">NTSE Particulars</th>
                        <th class="th-details">Details</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="criteria-name">Exam Name</td>
                        <td>National Talent Search Examination (NTSE)</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="criteria-name">Conducting Body</td>
                        <td>National Council of Educational Research and Training (NCERT)</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="criteria-name">Target Audience</td>
                        <td>Students studying in Class 10th</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="criteria-name">Exam Stages</td>
                        <td>Two Stages: Stage I (State/UT Level) and Stage II (National Level)</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="criteria-name">Exam Pattern</td>
                        <td>Two Papers: MAT (Mental Ability Test) and SAT (Scholastic Aptitude Test)</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="criteria-name">Exam Mode</td>
                        <td>Offline (Pen and Paper based)</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="criteria-name">Scholarship</td>
                        <td>Awarded to successful candidates from Class 11 up to Ph.D. level as per NCERT norms.</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="criteria-name">Selection Process</td>
                        <td>Candidates must clear Stage I to qualify for Stage II. Final selection is based on Stage II performance.</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>

        <div class="course-cta text-center">
            <h3>Ready to prove your talent at the National level?</h3>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Join Agrim Classes for NTSE <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<my-footer></my-footer>


<script src="footer.js"></script>

</body>